msgid "South Gate Technician"
msgstr "南門站技術員"

#: .\subway_professions.json
msgctxt "profession_female"
msgid "South Gate Technician"
msgstr "南門站技術員"

#. ~ Profession (male South Gate Technician) description
#: .\subway_professions.json
msgctxt "prof_desc_male"
msgid ""
"Seeking refuge away from the maelstrom of pain that is the New England "
"surface world, you decided to gain citizenship as a member of South Gate "
"Station. Amazingly, they actually accepted you. You had a natural aptitude "
"for various mechanical and life support systems for South Gate Station, and "
"took up training as a technician."
msgstr ""
"為了遠離新英格蘭地表世界的痛苦漩渦，你決定成為南門站的公民以尋求庇護。令人驚訝的是，他們竟然接納了你。你對南門站的各種機械和生命維持系統有著天生的才能，並接受了技術員的培訓。"

#. ~ Profession (female South Gate Technician) description
#: .\subway_professions.json
msgctxt "prof_desc_female"
msgid ""
"Seeking refuge away from the maelstrom of pain that is the New England "
"surface world, you decided to gain citizenship as a member of South Gate "
"Station. Amazingly, they actually accepted you. You had a natural aptitude "
"for various mechanical and life support systems for South Gate Station, and "
