#: .\Metro\NPCs\Talk_metro_redciv.json .\Metro\NPCs\Talk_metro_reichciv.json
#: .\UnderRail\NPCs\Talk_sgs_civ.json
msgid "Hello, What do you want from me?"
msgstr "你好，你想從我這裡得到什麼？"

#: .\Metro\NPCs\Talk_metro_redciv.json
#: .\Metro\NPCs\Talk_metro_redguardnpc.json
#: .\Metro\NPCs\Talk_metro_reichciv.json
#: .\Metro\NPCs\Talk_metro_reichsoldier.json
#: .\UnderRail\NPCs\Talk_sgs_civ.json .\UnderRail\NPCs\Talk_sgs_guardnpc.json
msgid "Hello, what do you want from me?"
msgstr "你好，你想從我這裡得到什麼？"

#: .\Metro\NPCs\Talk_metro_redciv.json
msgid "What's it like living as member of the Red Line?"
msgstr "作為紅線的一員生活是怎樣的？"

#: .\Metro\NPCs\Talk_metro_redciv.json
#: .\Metro\NPCs\Talk_metro_redguardnpc.json
#: .\Metro\NPCs\Talk_metro_reichciv.json
#: .\Metro\NPCs\Talk_metro_reichofficer.json
#: .\Metro\NPCs\Talk_metro_reichsoldier.json
#: .\UnderRail\NPCs\Talk_sgs_admin.json .\UnderRail\NPCs\Talk_sgs_civ.json
#: .\UnderRail\NPCs\Talk_sgs_guardnpc.json .\UnderRail\NPCs\Talk_sgs_pipe.json
msgid "Goodbye."
msgstr "再見。"

#: .\Metro\NPCs\Talk_metro_redciv.json
msgid ""
"Things can get pretty rough at times. I don't know what's worse, the "
"nosalises that threaten us outside the metro, or the commissars breathing "
"down our necks. I guess it's better than being dead, though."
msgstr "有時情況會變得相當艱難。我不知道什麼更糟，是地鐵外威脅我們的諾薩利斯，還是那些對我們虎視眈眈的政委。不過，我想這總比死了強。"

#: .\Metro\NPCs\Talk_metro_redciv.json
#: .\Metro\NPCs\Talk_metro_redguardnpc.json
#: .\Metro\NPCs\Talk_metro_reichciv.json
#: .\Metro\NPCs\Talk_metro_reichofficer.json
#: .\Metro\NPCs\Talk_metro_reichsoldier.json
#: .\UnderRail\NPCs\Talk_sgs_admin.json .\UnderRail\NPCs\Talk_sgs_civ.json
#: .\UnderRail\NPCs\Talk_sgs_guardnpc.json
msgid "Thanks for the info."
msgstr "謝謝你的信息。"

#: .\Metro\NPCs\Talk_metro_redguardnpc.json
#: .\Metro\NPCs\Talk_metro_reichsoldier.json
#: .\UnderRail\NPCs\Talk_sgs_guardnpc.json
msgid "Hello, Miss, What do you want from me?"
msgstr "你好，女士，你想從我這裡得到什麼？"

#: .\Metro\NPCs\Talk_metro_redguardnpc.json
msgid "How do you serve as a soldier of the Red line?"
msgstr "你如何作為一名紅線士兵服役？"

#: .\Metro\NPCs\Talk_metro_redguardnpc.json
msgid ""
"It's a duty I take with the utmost importance, there is no duty as solemn or"
" as important as being a standard bearer of the proletarian revolution. "
"Those Reich fascists and South Gate dogs will soon be welcomed into our "
"fold, with blood if need be!"
msgstr ""
"這是我肩負的最重要的職責，沒有比作為無產階級革命的旗手更莊嚴或更重要的職責了。那些帝國法西斯和南門走狗很快就會加入我們的行列，如果需要的話，就用鮮血來迎接他們！"

#: .\Metro\NPCs\Talk_metro_reichciv.json
msgid "What's it like living in the Reich?"
msgstr "在帝國生活是怎樣的？"

#: .\Metro\NPCs\Talk_metro_reichciv.json
msgid ""
"Unlike most of the metro, things are pretty clean here. The rules are a bit "
"too harsh at times though, and I'm often a bit fearful of the officers "
"around here. It's hard to parse fact from fiction when it comes to this war "
"with the reds."
msgstr ""
"與地鐵的大部分地方不同，這裡相當乾淨。不過規則有時有點太嚴厲了，我經常對這裡的軍官感到有點害怕。當涉及到與紅軍的這場戰爭時，很難分辨事實與虛構。"

#: .\Metro\NPCs\Talk_metro_reichofficer.json
msgid "Hello, Why do you think you're important enough to talk to me, woman?"
msgstr "你好，女人，你為什麼覺得自己有資格跟我說話？"

#: .\Metro\NPCs\Talk_metro_reichofficer.json
msgid "Hello, Why do you think you're important enough to talk to me."
msgstr "你好，你為什麼覺得自己有資格跟我說話。"

#: .\Metro\NPCs\Talk_metro_reichofficer.json
msgid "So you're an officer in the Reich? What's that like"
msgstr "所以你是帝國的一名軍官？那感覺如何"

#: .\Metro\NPCs\Talk_metro_reichofficer.json
msgid ""
"My task weighs heavily upon me at all times, the war with the Reds, that is."
" Managing the stations and the war at the same time can be taxing, even for "
"us Reich specimens. But I trust that we will win this war in the end."
msgstr ""
"我的任務始終沉重地壓在我身上，那就是與紅軍的戰爭。同時管理車站和戰爭可能很累人，即使對我們帝國精英來說也是如此。但我相信我們最終會贏得這場戰爭。"

#: .\Metro\NPCs\Talk_metro_reichsoldier.json
msgid "How do you serve as a soldier of the Reich?"
msgstr "你如何作為一名帝國士兵服役？"

#: .\Metro\NPCs\Talk_metro_reichsoldier.json
msgid ""
"There is no higher honor than to serve as a soldier of the Reich against the"
" hated reds. Our enemies are many, but they are all beneath us. Soon, all "
"the stations of the metro will be within our grasp, just you wait!"
msgstr "沒有比作為一名帝國士兵對抗可恨的紅軍更高的榮譽了。我們的敵人很多，但他們都低於我們。很快，地鐵的所有車站都將落入我們手中，你就等著瞧吧！"

#: .\Metro\NPCs\metro_doctor.json
msgid "Reich Doctor"
msgstr "帝國醫生"

#: .\Metro\NPCs\metro_doctor.json
msgid "I'm a doctor."
msgstr "我是一名醫生。"

#: .\Metro\NPCs\metro_doctor.json .\Metro\NPCs\metro_redmerchant.json
#: .\Metro\NPCs\metro_reichmerchant.json .\UnderRail\NPCs\sgs_cook.json
#: .\UnderRail\NPCs\sgs_doctor.json
msgid "Do you want anything from me? I'm a bit busy being at the moment."
msgstr "你想從我這裡得到什麼嗎？我現在有點忙。"

#: .\Metro\NPCs\metro_doctor.json .\Metro\NPCs\metro_redmerchant.json
#: .\Metro\NPCs\metro_reichmerchant.json
msgid "What is it like being a doctor in this metro?"
msgstr "在這個地鐵裡當醫生是怎樣的？"

#: .\Metro\NPCs\metro_doctor.json .\UnderRail\NPCs\sgs_doctor.json
msgid "Do you have any medical items for me?"
msgstr "你有什麼醫療物品給我嗎？"

#: .\Metro\NPCs\metro_doctor.json .\Metro\NPCs\metro_redmerchant.json
#: .\Metro\NPCs\metro_reichmerchant.json .\UnderRail\NPCs\sgs_cook.json
#: .\UnderRail\NPCs\sgs_doctor.json
msgid "Goodbye, thank you for your time."
msgstr "再見，謝謝你的時間。"

#: .\Metro\NPCs\metro_doctor.json
msgid ""
"Serving the Reich can be tedious at times, very, very, very tedious. "
"Sometimes I really do doubt myself, but the prospect of giving up when those"
" red bastards are still out there is too much to bear."
msgstr "為帝國服務有時可能很乏味，非常、非常、非常乏味。有時我真的懷疑自己，但當那些紅色混蛋還在外面時，放棄的前景實在難以承受。"

#: .\Metro\NPCs\metro_doctor.json .\Metro\NPCs\metro_redmerchant.json
#: .\Metro\NPCs\metro_reichmerchant.json .\UnderRail\NPCs\sgs_cook.json
#: .\UnderRail\NPCs\sgs_doctor.json .\UnderRail\NPCs\sgs_gun_merchant.json
msgid "Got it."
msgstr "明白了。"

#: .\Metro\NPCs\metro_redcivilian.json
msgid "Red Line Civilian"
msgstr "紅線平民"

#: .\Metro\NPCs\metro_redcivilian.json
msgid "A typical citizen of the Red Line."
msgstr "一個典型的紅線公民。"

#: .\Metro\NPCs\metro_redguard.json .\ticketcards\red_spawncard.json
msgid "Red Line Soldier"
msgstr "紅線士兵"

#: .\Metro\NPCs\metro_redguard.json .\Metro\NPCs\metro_reichheavy.json
#: .\Metro\NPCs\metro_reichsoldier.json .\UnderRail\NPCs\sgs_guard.json
#: .\UnderRail\NPCs\sgs_heavy_guard.json .\ticketcards\red_spawncard.json
#: .\ticketcards\reich_spawncard.json
msgid "Protects the station from assailants"
msgstr "保護車站免受襲擊者侵害"

#: .\Metro\NPCs\metro_redmerchant.json
msgid "Red Line Merchant"
msgstr "紅線商人"

#: .\Metro\NPCs\metro_redmerchant.json .\Metro\NPCs\metro_reichmerchant.json
msgid "I'm a merchant."
msgstr "我是一名商人。"

#: .\Metro\NPCs\metro_redmerchant.json .\Metro\NPCs\metro_reichmerchant.json
msgid "Do you have anything for me to buy?"
msgstr "你有什麼東西可以賣給我嗎？"

#: .\Metro\NPCs\metro_redmerchant.json
msgid ""
"Resources are tight, but we have more stuff than the reich. That much I can "
"say with certainty."
msgstr "資源緊張，但我們的東西比帝國多。這一點我可以肯定地說。"

#: .\Metro\NPCs\metro_reichciv.json
msgid "Reich Civilian"
msgstr "帝國平民"

#: .\Metro\NPCs\metro_reichciv.json
msgid "A typical citizen of the 4th Reich."
msgstr "一個典型的第四帝國公民。"

#: .\Metro\NPCs\metro_reichheavy.json
msgid "Reich Heavy Soldier"
msgstr "帝國重裝士兵"

#: .\Metro\NPCs\metro_reichmerchant.json
msgid "Reich Merchant"
msgstr "帝國商人"

#: .\Metro\NPCs\metro_reichmerchant.json
msgid ""
"Resources are tight, but we're better equipped than the reds. That much I "
"can say with certainty."
msgstr "資源緊張，但我們的裝備比紅軍好。這一點我可以肯定地說。"

#: .\Metro\NPCs\metro_reichoff.json
msgid "Reich Officer"
msgstr "帝國軍官"

#: .\Metro\NPCs\metro_reichoff.json
msgid "An officer of the 4th Reich."
msgstr "第四帝國的一名軍官。"

#: .\Metro\NPCs\metro_reichsoldier.json .\ticketcards\reich_spawncard.json
msgid "Reich Soldier"
msgstr "帝國士兵"

#: .\Metro\metro_armor\metro_armor.json
msgid "communist officer's hat"
msgid_plural "communist officer's hats"
msgstr[0] "共產主義軍官帽"

#. ~ Description for {'str': "communist officer's hat"}
#: .\Metro\metro_armor\metro_armor.json
msgid ""
"The only hat for a man of the proletarian revolution. Shoot dissidents, "
"reich fascists, dissidents and fascist dissidents disguised as civilians, "
"and look great doing it!"
msgstr "無產階級革命者的專屬帽子。用它來射殺異見分子、帝國法西斯分子、偽裝成平民的異見分子和法西斯異見分子，同時保持帥氣風範！"

#: .\Metro\metro_armor\metro_armor.json
msgid "communist officer's coat"
msgid_plural "communist officer's coats"
msgstr[0] "共產主義軍官外套"

#. ~ Description for {'str': "communist officer's coat"}
#: .\Metro\metro_armor\metro_armor.json
msgid ""
"A thick leather jacket.  Protects against the cold of the metro when the "
"warmth of the revolutionary spirit isn't enough."
msgstr "一件厚實的皮夾克。當革命精神的熱忱不足以抵禦地鐵的嚴寒時，它能提供保護。"

#: .\Metro\metro_armor\metro_armor.json
msgid "Red Line combat vest"
msgid_plural "Red Line combat vest"
msgstr[0] "紅線戰鬥背心"

#. ~ Use action holster_msg for {'str_sp': 'Red Line combat vest'}.
#. ~ Use action holster_msg for {'str_sp': '4th Reich combat vest'}.
#. ~ Use action holster_msg for {'str_sp': 'South Gate Station security
#. vest'}.
#: .\Metro\metro_armor\metro_armor.json
#: .\UnderRail\underrail_armor\sgs_armor.json
msgid "You stash your %s."
msgstr "你藏起了你的%s。"

#. ~ Use action holster_prompt for {'str_sp': 'Red Line combat vest'}.
#. ~ Use action holster_prompt for {'str_sp': '4th Reich combat vest'}.
#. ~ Use action holster_prompt for {'str_sp': 'South Gate Station security
#. vest'}.
#: .\Metro\metro_armor\metro_armor.json
#: .\UnderRail\underrail_armor\sgs_armor.json
msgid "Stash ammo"
msgstr "藏匿彈藥"

#. ~ Description for {'str_sp': 'Red Line combat vest'}
#: .\Metro\metro_armor\metro_armor.json
msgid ""
"A combat vest found in common use amongst the many soldiers of the red line."
" Relatively cheap to make, its low encumberance comes at the cost of having "
"relatively little ballistic protection."
msgstr "紅線眾多士兵中普遍使用的戰鬥背心。製作相對廉價，其低負重性以較弱的彈道防護為代價。"

#: .\Metro\metro_armor\metro_armor.json
msgid "Soviet flag"
msgid_plural "Soviet flags"
msgstr[0] "蘇聯國旗"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'Soviet flag'}
#: .\Metro\metro_armor\metro_armor.json
msgid "A large Soviet flag made to fly in even the worst conditions."
msgstr "一面大型蘇聯國旗，即使在最惡劣的條件下也能飄揚。"

#: .\Metro\metro_armor\metro_armor.json
msgid "Red Line Ushanka"
msgid_plural "Red Line Ushankas"
msgstr[0] "紅線烏沙帽"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'Red Line Ushanka'}
#: .\Metro\metro_armor\metro_armor.json
msgid ""
"A hat made from the pelts of animals.  Extremely warm. Often worn by the "
"citizens of the Red Line."
msgstr "用動物毛皮製成的帽子。極其保暖。常被紅線公民佩戴。"

#: .\Metro\metro_armor\metro_armor.json
msgid "4th Reich officer's hat"
msgid_plural "4th Reich officer's hats"
msgstr[0] "第四帝國軍官帽"

#. ~ Description for {'str': "4th Reich officer's hat"}
#: .\Metro\metro_armor\metro_armor.json
msgid ""
"Few can be deemed pure enough to be allowed entry into the Reich Stations. "
"Even fewer can become officers with an inflated sense of self importance."
msgstr "很少有人能被認定足夠純潔以獲准進入帝國車站。更少人能成為軍官，並懷有膨脹的自我重要感。"

#: .\Metro\metro_armor\metro_armor.json
msgid "4th Reich Formal Jacket"
msgid_plural "4th Reich Formal Jackets"
msgstr[0] "第四帝國正式夾克"

#. ~ Description for {'str': '4th Reich Formal Jacket'}
#: .\Metro\metro_armor\metro_armor.json
msgid ""
"An authoritative-looking jacket outfitted with a 4th Reich Armband. Common "
"amongst the higher ranking members of the 4th Reich stations."
msgstr "一件外觀威嚴的夾克，配有第四帝國臂章。常見於第四帝國車站的高級成員中。"

#: .\Metro\metro_armor\metro_armor.json
msgid "4th Reich combat vest"
msgid_plural "4th Reich combat vest"
msgstr[0] "第四帝國戰鬥背心"

#. ~ Description for {'str_sp': '4th Reich combat vest'}
#: .\Metro\metro_armor\metro_armor.json
msgid ""
"A combat vest found in common use amongst the well-trained, but somewhat "
"rare, members of the 4th Reich stations. Offers a relatively decent amount "
"of protection, at the cost of increased encumbrance."
msgstr "第四帝國車站訓練有素但較為稀少的成員中普遍使用的戰鬥背心。提供相對不錯的防護，代價是增加負重。"

#: .\Metro\metro_armor\metro_armor.json
msgid "4th Reich flag"
msgid_plural "4th Reich flags"
msgstr[0] "第四帝國國旗"

#. ~ Description for {'str': '4th Reich flag'}
#: .\Metro\metro_armor\metro_armor.json
msgid "A large Reich flag made to fly in even the worst conditions."
msgstr "一面大型帝國國旗，即使在最惡劣的條件下也能飄揚。"

#: .\Metro\metro_armor\metro_armor.json
msgid "4th Reich Heavy Armor"
msgid_plural "4th Reich Heavy Armors"
msgstr[0] "第四帝國重型護甲"

#. ~ Description for {'str': '4th Reich Heavy Armor'}
#: .\Metro\metro_armor\metro_armor.json
msgid ""
"Found only amongst the rarest of the rare Reich troops, this armor portends "
"doom for those of the Red Line who come across it. Outfitted with thick "
"metal plates, this armor is rather heavy."
msgstr "僅在極罕見的帝國部隊中發現，這件護甲預示著紅線成員遭遇它時的厄運。配備厚金屬板，相當沉重。"

#: .\Metro\metro_armor\metro_armor.json
msgid "Reich Stahlhelm"
msgid_plural "Reich Stahlhelms"
msgstr[0] "帝國鋼盔"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'Reich Stahlhelm'}
#: .\Metro\metro_armor\metro_armor.json
msgid ""
"A heavy steel helmet that provides excellent protection from all sorts of "
"damage.  How exactly people forced to live in the New England Metro got a "
"hold of these seemingly geniune articles is one of the great many mysteries "
"of the Cataclysm."
msgstr "一頂重型鋼盔，提供出色的全方位傷害防護。被迫生活在新英格蘭地鐵的人們如何獲得這些看似真品的頭盔，是大災變的眾多謎團之一。"

#: .\Metro\metro_weapons\metro_pistols.json
msgid "lolife magazine"
msgid_plural "lolife magazines"
msgstr[0] "洛萊夫彈匣"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'lolife magazine'}
#. ~ Description for {'str': 'lolife extended magazine'}
#: .\Metro\metro_weapons\metro_pistols.json
msgid ""
"A somehwat crude metal magazine for use with the common lolife pistol of the"
" metro."
msgstr "一個略顯粗糙的金屬彈匣，用於地鐵常見的洛萊夫手槍。"

#: .\Metro\metro_weapons\metro_pistols.json
msgid "lolife extended magazine"
msgid_plural "lolife extended magazines"
msgstr[0] "洛萊夫擴容彈匣"

#: .\Metro\metro_weapons\metro_pistols.json
msgid "Lolife"
msgid_plural "Lolife"
msgstr[0] "洛萊夫"

#: .\Metro\metro_weapons\metro_pistols.json
msgid ""
"The Lolife is a metro-made semi-automatic handgun with a standard eight-"
"round magazine chambered in .44 Magnum. As the Lolife is a metro-made "
"weapon, it has very little known history. It appears that Lolife has been "
"produced since at least 2023."
msgstr ""
"洛萊夫是一款地鐵製造的半自動手槍，標準八發彈匣，口徑為.44馬格南。由於是地鐵製造的武器，其歷史鮮為人知。似乎至少從2023年起就開始生產洛萊夫。"

#: .\Metro\metro_weapons\metro_rifles.json
msgid "Bastard magazine"
msgid_plural "Bastard magazines"
msgstr[0] "雜種卡賓槍彈匣"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'Bastard magazine'}
#: .\Metro\metro_weapons\metro_rifles.json
msgid "A crude magazine for the bastard carbine.  Holds 30 rounds."
msgstr "雜種卡賓槍的粗糙彈匣，可容納30發子彈。"

#: .\Metro\metro_weapons\metro_rifles.json
msgid "Kalash 2012 magazine"
msgid_plural "Kalash 2012 magazines"
msgstr[0] "卡拉什2012彈匣"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'Kalash 2012 magazine'}
#: .\Metro\metro_weapons\metro_rifles.json
msgid ""
"A standard magazine made for the Kalash 2012 rifle, made entirely of a "
"complex polymer.  Holds 40 rounds."
msgstr "為卡拉什2012步槍製造的標準彈匣，完全由複雜聚合物製成，可容納40發子彈。"

#: .\Metro\metro_weapons\metro_rifles.json
msgid "Bastard"
msgid_plural "Bastards"
msgstr[0] "雜種卡賓槍"

#: .\Metro\metro_weapons\metro_rifles.json
msgid ""
"The Bastard was one of the first Metro-made weapons. It is considerably "
"cheaper to make and maintain than other guns, needing relatively few parts "
"to create, making it ideal for weaponsmiths with few resources. This gun, "
"like most, has its ups and downs. It has a high rate of fire and holds 30 "
"rounds of ammunition, but fares poorly for sniping due to very poor accuracy"
" beyond a few yards."
msgstr ""
"雜種卡賓槍是地鐵最早製造的武器之一。與其他槍支相比，它的製造和維護成本要低得多，只需相對較少的零件即可製造，因此非常適合資源有限的武器匠。這把槍像大多數武器一樣，有其優缺點。它射速高，可容納30發彈藥，但由於幾碼外的精度極差，不適合狙擊。"

#: .\Metro\metro_weapons\metro_rifles.json
#: .\UnderRail\underrail_weapons\sgs_rifles.json
#: .\UnderRail\underrail_weapons\sgs_smg.json
msgid "semi-auto"
msgstr "半自動"

#: .\Metro\metro_weapons\metro_rifles.json
#: .\UnderRail\underrail_weapons\sgs_rifles.json
#: .\UnderRail\underrail_weapons\sgs_smg.json
msgid "auto"
msgstr "自動"

#: .\Metro\metro_weapons\metro_rifles.json
msgid "Kalash 2012"
msgid_plural "Kalash 2012s"
msgstr[0] "卡拉什2012"

#: .\Metro\metro_weapons\metro_rifles.json
msgid ""
"Kalash 2012 is one of the weapons in the Metro that predates the war and it "
"is highly prized. It's advanced polymer frame is rather unusual for Russian "
"weapons, but it seems to make a good account of itself."
msgstr "卡拉什2012是地鐵中戰前就存在的武器之一，備受珍視。其先進的聚合物槍身對於俄羅斯武器來說相當不尋常，但似乎表現不俗。"

#: .\Metro\metro_weapons\metro_rifles.json
msgid "2 rd."
msgstr "2發。"

#: .\Metro\metro_weapons\metro_rifles.json
msgid "shambler"
msgid_plural "shamblers"
msgstr[0] "蹣跚者"

#: .\Metro\metro_weapons\metro_rifles.json
msgid ""
"A shotgun modified to use a revolver cylinder mechanism, it can hold 6 "
"cartridges. Common among the denizens of the metro, and packs quite a punch."
msgstr "一種改裝為使用轉輪彈巢機構的霰彈槍，可容納6發彈藥。在地鐵居民中很常見，威力十足。"

#: .\UnderRail\sgs_ammo.json
msgid "5mm Standard Round"
msgid_plural "5mm Standard Rounds"
msgstr[0] "5毫米標準彈"

#: .\UnderRail\sgs_ammo.json
msgid "8.6mm Standard Round"
msgid_plural "8.6mm Standard Rounds"
msgstr[0] "8.6毫米標準彈"

#: .\UnderRail\sgs_ammo.json
